      <title>美国股票基金录得九个月来最大单周资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-equity-funds-draw-biggest-weekly-inflow-nine-months-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受华尔街持续上涨以及美联储今年晚些时候降息预期的提振，截至 3 月 20 日的 7 天内，美国股票基金需求强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-equity-funds-draw-biggest-weekly-inflow-nine-months-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 14:00:19 GMT</pubDate>
