      <title>加拿大一月份零售额下降； 2月份小幅反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/canadas-january-retail-sales-decline-slight-rebound-seen-february-2024-03-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五数据显示，受商品价格以及机动车辆及零部件销售下降的拖累，加拿大一月份零售额收缩幅度略低于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/canadas-january-retail-sales-decline-slight-rebound-seen-february-2024-03-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 12:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
